JST Compatible Cable Assembly

Full range of JST-compatible terminal wire assemblies offering the same quality and reliability as genuine JST connectors at significantly lower cost. Direct from our ISO 9001 certified factory.

Compatibility Notice: These are JST-compatible cable assemblies manufactured by Trycay. We are not affiliated with, authorized by, or using original JST components. All assemblies are produced to meet JST series specifications and are fully compatible with JST connectors.
